{"tid":1980923,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴城巴將於DSE期間恢復13條學校路線部分班次","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T06:22:00.000Z","uid":164435,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb5c8ce0b9c570ab30fa7b341cde3fdbfc91733","tid":1980923,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"Facebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/686033438811292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNWFBCitybus%2Fposts%2F686033438811292&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=ba5d8edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/686033438811292</a><br />\nPDF新聞稿 <a href=\"http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/tc/uploadedPressRelease/17829_20042020_school_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nwstbus.com.hk%2Ftc%2FuploadedPressRelease%2F17829_20042020_school_chi.pdf&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=eddaece0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/tc/uploadedPressRelease/17829_20042020_school_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【文憑試期間巴士服務安排🚌】<br />\n相信應屆文憑試考試喺呢幾個月都好努力備戰，終於嚟到考試嘅日子。<br />\n<br />\n為左方便大家前往考場應戰，新巴城巴將會恢復13條學校路線部分班次，儘量配合考生嘅需求。除此之外，9條路線亦會喺考試期間因應客量加強服務。有關路線嘅服務日期、開出時間，請參閱乘客通告！<br />\n<br />\n我哋都知道大家未必熟悉試場有咩巴士去到，所以我哋都整合咗唔同考場（學校）嘅到達路線，希望大家考試可以順順利利！最後祝大家科科5**！<br />\n<br />\n#新巴 #城巴 #NWFB #Citybus #配合中學文憑試考生前往考場 #恢復學校路線部分班次 #前往試場無煩惱 #文憑試 #減低考生考試壓力 #考試加油<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2dVZow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2dVZow.jpg&h=468420d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqK2Eox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqK2Eox.jpg&h=ea64b3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nStKSJy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnStKSJy.jpg&h=de1d2f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJS0q3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJS0q3y.jpg&h=6178533b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByQ9joy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByQ9joy.jpg&h=caf1c265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"fad03e3b9a980e2e806d9d45118434dd29038429","tid":1980923,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其中 7 個主科的考試日</span></strong>恢復 13 條學校路線的部份班次"},{"pid":"52db2252c3dbe6add1c56699b48e2dfee165b680","tid":1980923,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試周五開考 九巴恢復學校區巴士路線服務<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980945</a>"},{"pid":"5bf34d6ea67829e2958d324c258993661d3d94de","tid":1980923,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"hoenstly <br />\n考公開試真係最好搭mtr <br />\n第二日先罷啦<br />\n一陣中間塞車係㗎巴士度真係急到瀬尿<br />\n非常影響心理質素<br />\nu cant be late for a second"},{"pid":"a32b00f9412a6ebb07d8d1652481319955456a37","tid":1980923,"uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5bf34d6ea67829e2958d324c258993661d3d94de","tid":1980923,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"hoenstly <br />\n考公開試真係最好搭mtr <br />\n第二日先罷啦<br />\n一陣中間塞車係㗎巴士度真係急到瀬尿<br />\n非常影響心理質素<br />\nu cant be late for a second"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"港島唔少學校都係一定要搭巴士先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45edf4d316eb6adc772094667e08d066ccf6098","tid":1980923,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"比假希望學生<br />\n出曬notice話開足車<br />\n點知脫班脫到考生遲到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji